title: Jordan protests snowball over price hikes, income tax draft law
content: Hundreds of Jordanians demonstrated in the capital Amman for a third consecutive day yesterday against price hikes and an income tax draft law driven by IMF recommendations to slash its public debt.  Read on the original site
